Appcelerator Titanium Mobile Module Project
===========================================

Provide access to InfraRed emitter for Android (like SHV-E300S or Samsung galaxy Tab with IR emitter).


GET STARTED
------------

To compile module : 
1- 	Use "Build PATH > configure Build PATH > java build Path > Libraries > Add Externals JARS"
 	to add Android 21 (mine is under the directory "/Users/gtwin/Library/android-sdk-macosx/platforms/android-21").
2-  Update the  "build.properties" file to fit your configuration.
	Here is mine :
	titanium.platform=/Users/gtwin/Library/Application Support/Titanium/mobilesdk/osx/3.5.0.GA/android
	android.platform=/Users/gtwin/Library/android-sdk-macosx/platforms/android-21
	google.apis=/Users/gtwin/Library/android-sdk-macosx/add-ons/addon-google_apis-google-21
	android.ndk=/Users/gtwin/Documents/Titanium_Studio_Workspace/android-ndk-r10c